high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the leftmost head of lettuce off of the counter.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Wash the head of lettuce in the sink then pick it back up.
Turn around and begin walking to the door, then hang a right and walk over to the red trash bin in between the counter and white table.
Place the clean head of lettuce into the red trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce in the red trash bin.

high_descs: Turn and go left to face the counter to the right of the toaster.
Pick the lettuce on the left up from the counter.
Go to the right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sing, turn the water on and then off and pick the lettuce up from the sink.
Turn around and face the trash can on the right.
Put the lettuce in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put clean lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Walk forwards and then turn to your left so that you are facing the kitchen counter
Pick up a lettuce off of the counter
Turn around and then head to your left to face the sink
Put the lettuce in the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and then pick it back up
Turn around and then turn to your right to face the trash can
Throw the lettuce in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Rinse a lettuce and throw it away
